{"id": "1", "input_text": "“王大爷早啊，昨晚睡得怎么样？来，先测个血压。嗯……血压是一百三十八、八十二，稍微有点高啊。体温我看看，三十六度七，挺正常的。我看你这心电监护，心率七十五，呼吸十八次。一会儿记得把早饭吃了，药别忘了吃。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.7", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "75.0", "respiratoryRate": "18.0", "bloodPressure": "138/82", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": null, "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "2", "input_text": "“十二床李姐，手术回来三个小时了。现在感觉怎么样？刀口疼得厉害吗？血氧饱和度是九十八，挺好。心率快一点，九十二次，呼吸二十次。体温三十七度二，有点低热是正常的。皮肤切口我看了一下，目前是完好的，没有渗血。保持这个姿势别乱动啊。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "37.2", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "92.0", "respiratoryRate": "20.0", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": ["手术切口"], "catheter": null, "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "3", "input_text": "“检查一下十五床。患者目前处于嗜睡状态，能唤醒。来，看我手电筒。左侧瞳孔三毫米，对光反射灵敏；右侧瞳孔也是三毫米，对光反射灵敏。血压一百二十六、七十四，心率六十八。继续观察神志变化，要是发现呕吐立刻叫我。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "68.0", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "126/74", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "嗜睡", "skin": null, "catheter": null, "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "4", "input_text": "“张叔，今天觉得胸闷好点没？吸上氧气感觉怎么样？我看下，氧流量开的是每分钟两升。现在的血氧是九十四，呼吸频率还是快，二十四次。体温三十八度五，还在发烧。脉搏一百零二。这一瓶水吊完记得叫我，我再给你测个腋温。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "38.5", "pulseRate": "102.0", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": "24.0", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "5", "input_text": "“核对一下三号床的入量出量。家属，刚才那瓶生理盐水五百毫升已经输完了是吧？记录一下，静脉入量五百。我看下尿袋，尿量大概是三百五十毫升，颜色是淡黄色的，挺清亮。今天病人喝水了吗？记得喂点水，晚点我再来记总数。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": "尿管、静脉通路", "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": "异常", "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "6", "input_text": "“五零八房的老刘，今天空腹体重测了吗？七十二点五公斤是吧，比前天轻了点。来，手平放。血压是一百五、九十五，还是没降下来啊。脉搏八十五次。你这个降压药是不是没按时吃？心率挺整齐的，但血压得控制住，不然容易头晕。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": "85.0", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "150/95", "weight": "72.5", "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": null, "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "7", "input_text": "“接个班，急诊刚送来一位。男性，四十五岁。到达时意识模糊，BP九十、六十，脉搏一百一十，呼吸二十六。已经建立了静脉通道，目前正在吸氧。瞳孔是对称的，大概二点五左右，对光反射迟钝。病史提供人是家属，初步诊断是失血性休克。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": "失血性休克", "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": "110.0", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": "26.0", "bloodPressure": "90/60", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": "模糊", "skin": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "8", "input_text": "“阿婆，来量个体温。三十六度八，不烧了。心率是幺零八，怎么这么快？是不是刚才动弹了？呼吸二一次。血压是一百二、八十六。我看你这皮肤有点破损，是在哪儿蹭的吗？一会儿我给你涂点药。记得多喝温开水啊。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.8", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "108.0", "respiratoryRate": "21.0", "bloodPressure": "120/86", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": ["破损"], "catheter": null, "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "9", "input_text": "“小宝贝今天乖不乖呀？医生叔叔听听心跳。心率比较快，一百一十五次，小朋友紧张。体温三十九度幺，还是高热。呼吸三十次，肺部听诊有点杂音。家属记得多物理降温，要是还是烧得这么厉害，我们要考虑换个抗生素了。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "39.1", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "115.0", "respiratoryRate": "30.0", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": null, "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "10", "input_text": "“最后巡一下病房。二十号床，还没睡呢？血氧监控我看一下，九十六，正常。心率六十二，呼吸十六。我看你这引流袋，出量大概五十毫升，血性液体。体温刚才护士量过是三十七度。早点休息吧，有什么不舒服按床头铃。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "37.0", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "62.0", "respiratoryRate": "16.0", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": "引流管", "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "11", "input_text": "“二十八床，现在胸闷的感觉缓解点没？我看硝酸甘油泵入的速度是每小时三毫升。量下血压，一百一十、七十，比刚才降下来点。心率六十四次，挺稳的。如果待会儿觉得头晕或者心慌，一定要立刻按铃，药量我们再调。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "64.0", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "110/70", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "12", "input_text": "“王阿姨，测个餐后血糖啊。诶，十一点二，还是有点高。早上的诺和锐打了十二个单位对吧？体温正常，三十六度四。下午记得别吃水果了。我看你脚踝这儿有点水肿，平时坐着的时候把腿抬高一点。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.4", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": "11.2", "consciousness": null, "skin": ["其他"], "catheter": null, "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "13", "input_text": "“一号床，今天开始输头孢曲松了，观察一下有没有皮疹或者胸闷。体温还是高，三十八度九，心率九十五。呼吸频率二十二次，血氧九十三，稍微低了点，把氧气流量调到三升每分钟。痰咳得出来吗？颜色是什么样的？”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "38.9", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "95.0", "respiratoryRate": "22.0", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "14", "input_text": "“七床，今天还恶心吗？这瓶潘托拉唑是保护胃黏膜的，点滴速度别自己调啊。血压一百零五、六十五，脉搏七十二。昨晚到现在一共喝了五百毫升水，记录一下。我看尿色有点深，还得再多补点液。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": "72.0", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "105/65", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": "静脉通路", "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "15", "input_text": "“老张，把手握紧我看看。嗯，左边还是没劲。昨晚吃的阿司匹林和阿托伐他汀没反应吧？瞳孔两点五毫米，对光反射灵敏。血压一百四十二、九十，心率七十八。一定要按时吃药，预防血栓再次形成。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "78.0", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "142/90", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": null, "limbActivity": "异常", "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "16", "input_text": "“十六床，早上给你打了一针呋塞米。刚才那两个小时尿了多少？六百毫升是吧，好，记录在出量里。体重今天测的是六十八公斤。血压一百三十五、八十五。注意听，如果觉得耳朵响或者身上没力气，及时跟我们说。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "135/85", "weight": "68.0", "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": null, "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "17", "input_text": "“四十五床，手术后止痛泵带着呢吧？要是还觉得疼，我们刚才加了地佐辛。测下呼吸，十四次，稍微有点慢，要注意。心率八十二，血氧九十九。我看你这引流管里是淡红色的液体，量不多，大概三十毫升，先观察。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "82.0", "respiratoryRate": "14.0", "bloodPressure": null, "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": "止痛泵、引流管", "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "18", "input_text": "“快，建立双通路！心率掉到四十了，推一毫克肾上腺素！血压七十、四十，赶紧挂上多巴胺，每小时十毫克泵入。准备气管插管。血氧测不到，快，心肺复苏别停！记录时间，十四点一十分。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 14:10:00", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "40.0", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "70/40", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": "静脉通路、气管插管", "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "19", "input_text": "“十二床，明天手术。刚才给你皮下注射了低分子肝素，预防血栓的。血压一百二十八、七十二，心率七十。体温三十六度六，没发烧。晚八点以后就不要吃东西了，水也少喝，听清楚了吗？”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": "36.6", "pulseRate": null, "heartRate": "70.0", "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "128/72", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": null, "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
{"id": "20", "input_text": "“陈大爷，这颗是地高辛，专门稳心率的；那颗是氨氯地平，降压用的。别吃混了。我看下现在的脉搏，六十八次，挺规律的。血压一百三、八十，控制得不错。记得药要用温开水送服，别用茶水啊。”", "raw_output": null, "reasoning_output": null, "cleaned_json": {"assessmentTime": "2026-02-01 10:02:03", "education": null, "ethnicity": null, "admissionTime": null, "admissionMethod": null, "diagnosis": null, "allergyHistory": null, "temperature": null, "pulseRate": "68.0", "heartRate": null, "respiratoryRate": null, "bloodPressure": "130/80", "weight": null, "height": null, "bloodSugar": null, "consciousness": null, "skin": null, "catheter": null, "limbActivity": null, "diet": null, "sleep": null, "urination": null, "defecation": null, "stoolFrequency": null}, "model_used": "openai", "missed_keys": null, "appended_keys": null}
